Astrologist: {
	DisplayName: Astrologist

	TownNPCMood: {
		Content: Don't know about the others, but I'm fine with everything.
		NoHome: A little house, please? ...shouldn't I come to you for that?
		FarFromHome: I know certain someone loves to sleep outside, but I prefer to have a wooden box of my own.
		LoveSpace: I haven't had that much space since... Boy, I've NEVER had that much space!
		DislikeCrowded: Get rid of the crowd, please.
		HateCrowded: So cramped in here, it's like I'm back on the Nexus.
		LoveBiome: I love {BiomeName}. The sky is the clearest here!
		LikeBiome: "{BiomeName}... There aren't any attractive wizards here, but it's not bad either."
		DislikeBiome: "{BiomeName} is not my thing. I confuse snow with stars."
		HateBiome: "{BiomeName}?! Count me out!"
		LoveNPC: "{NPCName}... Now HE's got some aura."
		LikeNPC: I like {NPCName}. Old people are the best!
		DislikeNPC: "{NPCName} Kinda annoys me."
		HateNPC: "{NPCName} is a walking reminder of everything I didn't like about the Nexus."
		LikeNPC_Princess: "{NPCName}? Well, ain't she just adorable?"
		Princess_LovesNPC: "{NPCName} - now she's something else!"
	}

	Census.SpawnCondition: Conditions unknown
}

