Collector: {
	DisplayName: Collector

	TownNPCMood: {
		Content: It ain't that bad, I guess. Congratulations.
		NoHome: Am I supposed to sleep on the grass? My poor back...
		FarFromHome: How far am I supposed to walk? Uhh, can't you just order space uber for me or something?
		LoveSpace: It's desolate out there, just the way I like it.
		DislikeCrowded: There's too many people here. People who don't take my orders.
		HateCrowded: Too many people making fun of me around, it's horrible!
		LoveBiome: "{BiomeName} makes me feel right at home."
		LikeBiome: You know, {BiomeName} ain't that bad.
		DislikeBiome: Ugh, {BiomeName}, it stinks out there.
		HateBiome: "{BiomeName}? I should evacuate immediately."
		LoveNPC: Love {NPCName}! I hate Christmas too!
		LikeNPC: "{NPCName} is a good fella. He's got money!"
		DislikeNPC: This world would look much better without grass, and {NPCName} has to agree with me!
		HateNPC: "{NPCName} has no idea what he's talking about. No one understands Terraria better than me!"
		LikeNPC_Princess: Pfft... {NPCName} seriously thinks she's better than everyone?
		Princess_LovesNPC: "{NPCName}... Please, not now."
	}

	Census.SpawnCondition: Conditions unknown
	RecipeBrowser.ExchangeTip: Exchange with Genoshi
}

CollectorTeleport.DisplayName: Genoshi

Commando: {
	DisplayName: Commando

	Names: {
		0: Ooo
		1: Grey
		2: Ford
		3: Zaphod
		4: Douglas
		5: Marvin
		6: Slartibartfast
	}

	TownNPCMood: {
		Content: After all this time, I can confidently say... I feel good!
		NoHome: I know I'm not in the best position right now... But I can hope for a shelter, right?
		FarFromHome: Oh, shoot! Hope I'm not lost again!
		LoveSpace: It's so spacious here! Suspiciously spacious...
		DislikeCrowded: Have there always been so many people here, or it's just me?
		HateCrowded: I'm afraid even a space suit won't protect me from how quickly the air is being used up here...
		LoveBiome: I love {BiomeName}. Snowflakes remind me of the stars!
		LikeBiome: I like {BiomeName}. It's just like Mars!
		DislikeBiome: "{BiomeName}... It's too weird here, even for me."
		HateBiome: "{BiomeName} scares me, I think I saw that spying drone again..."
		LoveNPC: "{NPCName} understands me like no one else... He's as much a traitor as I am!"
		LikeNPC: "{NPCName} always finds a common ground with people who don't look like people..."
		DislikeNPC: It's hard for me to choose someone I don't like, but if no one likes {NPCName}, then neither do I.
		HateNPC: Please explain to Santa that I'm not going to steal Christmas! That was not a part of my mission!
		LikeNPC_Princess: "{NPCName} believes that everyone deserves happiness. Even aliens like me!"
		Princess_LovesNPC: "{NPCName} is the friend we've been missing all along!"
	}

	Start: Oh, I'm so sorry.. There are so many wholesome people in your world, all these meetings, parties, games, and you're always so cheerful, so.. naive.. On my home planet, you could only dream of such a peaceful life. I just wanted to be a part of your big family!
	BloodMoon: It's kinda scary outside. I thought brain eating went out of human fashion a couple of centuries ago.
	Party: I'm tired of everyone offering me a drink. Like I can just remove my space helmet to taste it without dying from oxygen poisoning!

	Talk: {
		0: Aloha! Isn't that how you, humans, greet each other?
		1: Oh, here you are! Do you need something?
		2: If a robot repairs another robot, would you rather call it a mechanic or a doctor?.. Oh, hi there! Sorry, I've been thinking...
	}

	Census.SpawnCondition: Conditions unknown
}

