Shutterbug: {
	DisplayName: Shutterbug

	TownNPCMood: {
		Content: Eh. Could be worse.
		NoHome: Would be sweet to have my own living space.
		LoveSpace: I appreciate quiet.
		FarFromHome: Doesn't look like a house to me.
		DislikeCrowded: Can you take all these loafers somewhere far, far away?
		HateCrowded: There are too many people here. How many content mods have you installed?!
		LoveBiome: Love {BiomeName}. If I live here, I'll catch your eye more often, which means you won't forget to take more clips and get rewards.
		LikeBiome: Sure, {BiomeName} is one of the biomes.
		DislikeBiome: You know, I'm pretty sure there is some clever and logical reason why I don't like {BiomeName}. I just haven't figured it out yet.
		HateBiome: Oh, {BiomeName}... Should I even begin?
		LikeNPC: "{NPCName} is cool. Bet we share the same political views."
		DislikeNPC: Of all the guests from other worlds, {NPCName} makes the least sense.
		HateNPC: And... I can't stand tall people. Seriously, if {NPCName} calls me baby doll again, I'll exterminate her!
		LoveNPC: I love {NPCName}.
		LikeNPC_Princess: I like {NPCName}.
		Princess_LovesNPC: I like {NPCName}.
	}

