TheSpirit: {
	DisplayName: The Spirit

	Dialogues: {
		Call: Connecting... Please, stay on the line...
		Summon_1: The Spirit has joined!
		Summon_2: The Spirit has arrived!
		Downed: The Spirit has been defeated!
		Treat_1: Stop right there, criminal scum, and prepare for justice!
		Treat_2: Oh shoes, my transmitter is dead! Do you even know how expensive this stuff is these days?
		Treat_3: I'll report that! I'll report everything!
		Escape: <Spirit> Good night, everybody!
	}

	Confusion: Spirit is... perplexed?

	DefeatDialogues: {
		Start: I thought it would be easier... Hey, you don't look like a space pirate! Of course you're not! Did I... Ooh! I just got it all mixed up?... But my transmitter got a signal from here... Now it's absolutely irretrievably destroyed! How do I get back now...
		StartConfirm: I'm sorry...

		Talk: {
			0: The carbon-based life-form is trying to relate to me. What should I do?
			1: I'm in the middle of something...
			2: Don't mind me, I'm just waiting for some thought to cross my mind.
			3: Do you hear this music? Sounds kinda ominous, like something serious is gonna happen.
			4: So many answers and so few questions!
		}
	}
}

