Angler: {
	QuestFish: {
		AuroraBorealis: Aurora borealis? At this time of year? At this time of day? Localized entirely in my fishbowl? Oh yeah, make sure that happens! It will make the most beautiful night light the world has ever seen.
		Blockfish: I don't know where this ship came from, but the energy coming from it causes all living things in the area to turn into ice! It's simply impossible for me to fish in such conditions, good to have you around. If you catch anything, bring it to me, and I'll reward you.
	}

	FishLocation.StrandedShip: Caught in the Stranded Ship
}

